delete_metric_run(25.10)                              delete_metric_run(25.10)

Name delete_metric_run - Deletes the specified metric run
Syntax
Parameters  -help  Outputs  a brief description that includes type and default
       information for each delete_metric_run parameter. For  a  detailed  de-
       scription  of  the  command and all of its parameters, use the man com-
       mand: man delete_metric_run -name <metric_name> Name of the metric  run
       to  be  deleted.  It defaults to the current run. This parameter corre-
       sponds to the -id parameter  of  the  read_metric  command.  Data_type:
       string, optional
Example
